<ul>
<li><cite style="font-style:normal" class="" id="CITEREFLende_DH.2C_Smith_EO2002">Lende DH, Smith EO (April 2002). "<a href="http://www.blackwell-synergy.com/openurl?genre=article&amp;sid=nlm:pubmed&amp;issn=0965-2140&amp;date=2002&amp;volume=97&amp;issue=4&amp;spage=447" class="external text" title="http://www.blackwell-synergy.com/openurl?genre=article&amp;sid=nlm:pubmed&amp;issn=0965-2140&amp;date=2002&amp;volume=97&amp;issue=4&amp;spage=447" rel="nofollow">Evolution meets biopsychosociality: an analysis of addictive behavior</a>". <i>Addiction</i> <b>97</b> (4): 447–58. <a href="http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/11964060" class="external" title="http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/11964060">PMID 11964060</a><span class="printonly">. <a href="http://www.blackwell-synergy.com/openurl?genre=article&amp;sid=nlm:pubmed&amp;issn=0965-2140&amp;date=2002&amp;volume=97&amp;issue=4&amp;spage=447" class="external free" title="http://www.blackwell-synergy.com/openurl?genre=article&amp;sid=nlm:pubmed&amp;issn=0965-2140&amp;date=2002&amp;volume=97&amp;issue=4&amp;spage=447" rel="nofollow">http://www.blackwell-synergy.com/openurl?genre=article&amp;sid=nlm:pubmed&amp;issn=0965-2140&amp;date=2002&amp;volume=97&amp;issue=4&amp;spage=447</a></span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.atitle=Evolution+meets+biopsychosociality%3A+an+analysis+of+addictive+behavior&amp;rft.jtitle=Addiction&amp;rft.aulast=Lende+DH%2C+Smith+EO&amp;rft.au=Lende+DH%2C+Smith+EO&amp;rft.date=April+2002&amp;rft.volume=97&amp;rft.issue=4&amp;rft.pages=447%E2%80%9358&amp;rft_id=info:pmid/11964060&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.blackwell-synergy.com%2Fopenurl%3Fgenre%3Darticle%26sid%3Dnlm%3Apubmed%26issn%3D0965-2140%26date%3D2002%26volume%3D97%26issue%3D4%26spage%3D447&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Addiction"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
<li>Ornstein, C., (2005-11-14). <a href="http://www.uchc.edu/ocomm/newsarchive/news05/nov05/meth.html" class="external text" title="http://www.uchc.edu/ocomm/newsarchive/news05/nov05/meth.html" rel="nofollow">Quitting meth pays off</a>. <i>LA Times</i>.</li>
</ul>
